<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Error - 标签 - w23ta0's blog</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/tags/error/</link><description>You got a dream, you gotta protect it.</description><generator>Hugo 0.145.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</managingEditor><webMaster>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:23:13 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://w23ta0.github.io/tags/error/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>解决LDAP出现ldap_bind: Invalid credentials (49)错误</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20170314-%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3ldap%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0ldap-bind-invalid-credentials-49-%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/</link><pubDate>Tue, 14 Mar 2017 14:43:23 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20170314-%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3ldap%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0ldap-bind-invalid-credentials-49-%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81/">身份认证</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/ldap/">LDAP</category><description>&lt;p>LDAP最经常遇到的就是ldap_bind: Invalid credentials (49)错误，本文阐述了错误原因及解决办法：
比如在某LDAP客户端，使用rootdn(管理员)权限为某用户修改密码时&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ ldappasswd -H ldap://172.16.0.21 -x -D &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;cn=admin,ou=People,dc=expmale,dc=com&amp;#34;&lt;/span> -W -S &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;uid=zhang3,ou=People,dc=expmale,dc=com&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">New password: 
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Re-enter new password: 
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Enter LDAP Password: 
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ldap_bind: Invalid credentials &lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>49&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>错误原因1：管理员DN或者用户DN错误&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>管理员DN是在&lt;code>/etc/openldap/slapd.conf&lt;/code>中指定的rootdn，其格式
应该是”cn=admin,dc=expmale,dc=com”
而不是”cn=admin,ou=People,dc=expmale,dc=com”
而普通用户的DN才应该是”uid=zhang3,ou=People,dc=expmale,dc=com”。
也可以执行如下命令查看该用户的DN是否存在&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>